<plot>Ole Olsen and Chic Johnson are celebrating their 35th-year together in shown-business, and Ralph Staub drops by and visits them. Then Ralph, and his camera, drive to a Las Vegas golf course, where Johnny Weissmuller, Gordon MacRae, Chill Wills and Gene Autry are playing together in a foursome, and admiring each other's putts and driving. The short-game is ignored. Henny Youngman, between sets at a club, drops by and asks them to take his wife...please.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?482134</url></doc>
